    <title>Python基础类型和运算符</title>
    <link href="/2022/07/15/love-chaichai/"/>
    <url>/2022/07/15/love-chaichai/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="基础的数据类型"><a href="#基础的数据类型" class="headerlink" title="基础的数据类型"></a>基础的数据类型</h3><ul><li><code>Number</code>(数字类型)</li><li><code>String</code>(字符串类型)</li><li><code>List</code>(列表类型)</li><li><code>Tuple</code>(元组类型)</li><li><code>Dictionary</code>(字典类型)</li></ul><p>其中 <strong>数字类型</strong> 又分为:</p><ul><li>整形: (在<code>python 2.x</code>中有<code>int</code>和<code>long</code>两种类型, 但是这种区分对<code>python</code>区分不大, 在<code>python 3.x</code>中整数只有一种<code>int</code>, 删除了<code>long</code>, （如<code>0b100</code>，换算成十进制是<code>4</code>）、八进制（如<code>0o100</code>，换算成十进制是<code>64</code>）、十进制（<code>100</code>）和十六进制（<code>0x100</code>，换算成十进制是<code>256</code>）的表示法</li><li>浮点类型: 浮点数也就是小数，之所以称为浮点数，是因为按照科学记数法表示时，一个浮点数的小数点位置是可变的，浮点数除了数学写法（如<code>123.456</code>）之外还支持科学计数法（如<code>1.23456e2</code>）</li><li>复数类型:形如<code>3+5j</code>，跟数学上的复数表示一样，唯一不同的是虚部的<code>i</code>换成了<code>j</code></li><li>布尔类型: 布尔值只有<code>True</code>、<code>False</code>两种值，要么是<code>True</code>，要么是<code>False</code>，在<code>Python</code>中，可以直接用<code>True</code>、<code>False</code>表示布尔值（请注意大小写），也可以通过布尔运算计算出来（例如<code>3 &lt; 5</code>会产生布尔值<code>True</code>，而<code>2 == 1</code>会产生布尔值<code>False</code>）。</li></ul><p><strong>字符串类型:</strong><br>&amp;emsp;&amp;emsp;字符串是以单引号或双引号括起来的任意文本，比如<code>&#39;hello&#39;</code>和<code>&quot;hello&quot;</code>,字符串还有原始字符串表示法、字节字符串表示法、<code>Unicode</code>字符串表示法，而且可以书写成多行的形式（用三个单引号或三个双引号开头，三个单引号或三个双引号结尾）。</p><blockquote><p>如:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;stc = &quot;&quot;&quot;this is a test1</span><br><span class="line">        this is a test2&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">&gt;print(stc)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><p><code>python</code>的字串列表有2种取值顺序:</p><ul><li>从左到右索引默认0开始的，最大范围是字符串长度少1</li><li>从右到左索引默认-1开始的，最大范围是字符串开头</li></ul><hr><h3 id="变量的命名"><a href="#变量的命名" class="headerlink" title="变量的命名"></a>变量的命名</h3><ul><li>硬性规则<ul><li>变量名由字母（广义的<code>Unicode</code>字符，不包括特殊字符）、数字和下划线构成，数字不能开头</li><li>大小写敏感（大写的a和小写的A是两个不同的变量）。</li><li>不要跟关键字（有特殊含义的单词，后面会讲到）和系统保留字（如函数、模块等的名字）冲突。</li></ul></li><li>PEP 8要求<ul><li>用小写字母拼写，多个单词用下划线连接。</li><li>受保护的实例属性用单个下划线开头</li><li>私有的实例属性用两个下划线开头</li></ul></li></ul><h5 id="示例"><a href="#示例" class="headerlink" title="示例:"></a>示例:</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a = 123  // 整数类型</span><br><span class="line">a = 0b10 //二进制表示法</span><br><span class="line">a = 0x10 // 十六进制表示</span><br><span class="line">a = 0o10 // 八进制表示</span><br><span class="line">a = 10   // 十进制表示</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">b = 12.3 //浮点数类型</span><br><span class="line">b = 12.3e2 //表示科学计数法1230, 及12.3X10X10 </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">c = &quot;this is a test&quot; //字符串类型</span><br><span class="line">c = &#x27;this is a test&#x27;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">d = True //布尔类型</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">e = 1 + 2j //复数类型</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Python中关键字"><a href="#Python中关键字" class="headerlink" title="Python中关键字"></a>Python中关键字</h3><blockquote><p>保留字即关键字，我们不能把它们用作任何标识符名称。<code>Python</code> 的标准库提供了一个 keyword 模块，可以输出当前版本的所有关键字：</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">import keyword</span><br><span class="line">lst = keyword.kwlist</span><br><span class="line">print(lst)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出结果为:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[&#x27;False&#x27;, &#x27;None&#x27;, &#x27;True&#x27;, &#x27;and&#x27;, &#x27;as&#x27;, &#x27;assert&#x27;, &#x27;break&#x27;, &#x27;class&#x27;, &#x27;continue&#x27;, &#x27;def&#x27;, &#x27;del&#x27;, &#x27;elif&#x27;, &#x27;else&#x27;, &#x27;except&#x27;, &#x27;finally&#x27;, &#x27;for&#x27;, &#x27;from&#x27;, &#x27;global&#x27;, &#x27;if&#x27;, &#x27;import&#x27;, &#x27;in&#x27;, &#x27;is&#x27;, &#x27;lambda&#x27;, &#x27;nonlocal&#x27;, &#x27;not&#x27;, &#x27;or&#x27;, &#x27;pass&#x27;, &#x27;raise&#x27;, &#x27;return&#x27;, &#x27;try&#x27;, &#x27;while&#x27;, &#x27;with&#x27;, &#x27;yield&#x27;]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h5 id="变量类型转换"><a href="#变量类型转换" class="headerlink" title="变量类型转换"></a>变量类型转换</h5><blockquote><p>在对变量类型进行转换时可以使用Python的内置函数（准确的说下面列出的并不是真正意义上的函数，而是后面我们要讲到的创建对象的构造方法）。</p></blockquote><ul><li><code>int()</code>: 将一个数值或字符串转换成整数，可以指定进制</li><li><code>float()</code>：将一个字符串转换成浮点数。</li><li><code>str()</code>：将指定的对象转换成字符串形式，可以指定编码</li><li><code>chr()</code>：将整数转换成该编码对应的字符串（一个字符）。</li><li><code>ord()</code>：将字符串（一个字符）转换成对应的编码（整数）。</li></ul><h5 id="示例-1"><a href="#示例-1" class="headerlink" title="示例"></a>示例</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a = int(123)</span><br><span class="line">b = float(123)</span><br><span class="line">c = str(&#x27;hello&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">d = chr(123) #将整型的123转为字符</span><br><span class="line">e = ord(&#x27;G&#x27;) #将ASCII的字符G转为int类型编码值</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">print(a)</span><br><span class="line">print(b)</span><br><span class="line">print(c)</span><br><span class="line">print(d)</span><br><span class="line">print(e)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出结果:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">123</span><br><span class="line">123.0</span><br><span class="line">hello</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="运算符"><a href="#运算符" class="headerlink" title="运算符"></a>运算符</h3><blockquote><p>Python支持多种运算符，下表大致按照优先级从高到低的顺序列出了所有的运算符，我们会陆续使用到它们。</p></blockquote><table><thead><tr><th>运算符</th><th>描述</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>[]</code> <code>[:]</code></td><td>下标，切片</td></tr><tr><td><code>**</code></td><td>指数</td></tr><tr><td><code>~</code> <code>+</code> <code>-</code></td><td>按位取反, 正负号</td></tr><tr><td><code>*</code> <code>/</code> <code>%</code> <code>//</code></td><td>乘，除，模，整除</td></tr><tr><td><code>+</code> <code>-</code></td><td>加，减</td></tr><tr><td><code>&gt;&gt;</code> <code>&lt;&lt;</code></td><td>右移，左移</td></tr><tr><td><code>&amp;</code></td><td>按位与</td></tr><tr><td><code>^</code> <code>|</code></td><td>按位异或，按位或</td></tr><tr><td><code>&lt;=</code> <code>&lt;</code> <code>&gt;</code> <code>&gt;=</code></td><td>小于等于，小于，大于，大于等于</td></tr><tr><td><code>==</code> <code>!=</code></td><td>等于，不等于</td></tr><tr><td><code>is</code>  <code>is not</code></td><td>身份运算符</td></tr><tr><td><code>in</code> <code>not in</code></td><td>成员运算符</td></tr><tr><td><code>not</code> <code>or</code> <code>and</code></td><td>逻辑运算符</td></tr><tr><td><code>=</code> <code>+=</code> <code>-=</code> <code>*=</code> <code>/=</code> <code>%=</code> <code>//=</code> <code>**=</code> <code>&amp;=</code> <code>|=</code> <code>^=</code> <code>&gt;&gt;=</code> <code>&lt;&lt;=</code></td><td>（复合）赋值运算符</td></tr></tbody></table><blockquote><p><strong>说明：</strong> 在实际开发中，如果搞不清楚运算符的优先级，可以使用括号来确保运算的执行顺序。</p></blockquote><hr><p><strong>Note:</strong></p><ul><li><p><code>print</code>格式化输出的几种方式</p><ul><li>直接输出, 无其他类型数据<ul><li><code>print(&#39;hello&#39;)</code></li><li><code>print(a)  # a是一个int类型数据</code></li></ul></li><li>和其他类型输出结合输出<ul><li><code>print(&quot;hello&quot;, a, b) # a,b分别是一个int类型数据5, 10, 输出结果未hello 5 10, 自动生成一个空格</code> </li><li><code>print(f&quot;hello&#123;a&#125;&quot;, a) # 假设a是int类型值为5, 则结果为hello5, 这种仅仅在python 2.x上支持</code></li><li><code>print(&quot;r:%.2d l:%.3f&quot;%(10, 12)) #结果为r:10 l:12.000, 浮点数.3f表示三位小数位, d表示整形输出, f表示浮点输出</code></li></ul></li></ul></li><li><p><code>type</code>功能函数</p><ul><li>获取一个变量的类型<ul><li><code>print(type(123)) //输出结果为 &lt;class &#39;int&#39;&gt;</code>   </li><li><code>print(type(&quot;hello&quot;)) //输出结果为&lt;class &#39;str&#39;&gt;, 表示为str类型</code></li></ul></li></ul></li><li><p><code>del</code>删除一个变量</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">var = 10</span><br><span class="line">var1 = 20</span><br><span class="line">print(var)</span><br><span class="line">del var, var1</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">var = 20</span><br><span class="line">del var</span><br><span class="line">print(var) # error: name &#x27;var&#x27; is not defined</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><code>python</code>对变量的重新赋值会改变内存地址</p></li></ul><hr><p><em><strong>测试代码</strong></em></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br><span class="line">78</span><br><span class="line">79</span><br><span class="line">80</span><br><span class="line">81</span><br><span class="line">82</span><br><span class="line">83</span><br><span class="line">84</span><br><span class="line">85</span><br><span class="line">86</span><br><span class="line">87</span><br><span class="line">88</span><br><span class="line">89</span><br><span class="line">90</span><br><span class="line">91</span><br><span class="line">92</span><br><span class="line">93</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># b = long(123)</span><br><span class="line"># print(type(b))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">strc = &quot;&quot;&quot;this is a test</span><br><span class="line">do you know</span><br><span class="line">hello world</span><br><span class="line">no end test&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">print(strc)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">a = int(123)</span><br><span class="line">b = float(123)</span><br><span class="line">c = str(&#x27;hello&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">d = chr(123)</span><br><span class="line">e = ord(&#x27;G&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">print(a)</span><br><span class="line">print(b)</span><br><span class="line">print(c)</span><br><span class="line">print(d)</span><br><span class="line">print(e)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">a = 3&amp;2</span><br><span class="line">print(a)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">print(&quot;r:%.2d l:%.5f&quot; %(100, 12.3))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">print(type(&quot;hello&quot;))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">/////////////////////////////////////</span><br><span class="line">a =&#x27;hello&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">b =&quot;heallo&quot;</span><br><span class="line">print(a)</span><br><span class="line">print(b)</span><br><span class="line">print(&quot;welcom&quot;, a, b)</span><br><span class="line">#print(f&quot;welcom &#123;a&#125;&quot;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">f = True</span><br><span class="line">print(f)</span><br><span class="line">print(&quot;welcom&quot;, b)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 运算符</span><br><span class="line">print(1+2)</span><br><span class="line">print(1-2)</span><br><span class="line">print(2*2)</span><br><span class="line">print(14/5)</span><br><span class="line">print(14//5)</span><br><span class="line">print(14%5)</span><br><span class="line">print(14**5)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># g = int(2.8)</span><br><span class="line"># print(g)</span><br><span class="line"># print(type(g))</span><br><span class="line"># g = str(input(&quot;string&quot;))</span><br><span class="line"># print(g)</span><br><span class="line"># print(type(g))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># g = chr(int(input(&quot;char&quot;)))</span><br><span class="line"># print(g)</span><br><span class="line"># print(type(g))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># g = ord(str(input(&quot;char&quot;)))</span><br><span class="line"># print(g)</span><br><span class="line"># print(type(g))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">print(-1&gt;&gt;1)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">a = 10</span><br><span class="line">a *= 2</span><br><span class="line">print(a)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">print(&quot;a =&quot;, a)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">print(&quot;a = &quot;, a)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">print(a is True)</span><br><span class="line">print(a is not False)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># tmp =int(input(&quot;请输入温度:&quot;))</span><br><span class="line"># res =(tmp - 32) / 1.8</span><br><span class="line"># print(&quot;%.1f华氏度 = %5.2f摄氏度&quot; % (tmp,res))</span><br><span class="line"># print(&quot;%.1f华氏度 = %05.2f摄氏度&quot; % (tmp,res))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 计算圆的面积周长</span><br><span class="line"># r = float(input(&quot;输入圆的半径:&quot;))</span><br><span class="line"># area = 3.14*(r**2)</span><br><span class="line"># len =2*3.14*r</span><br><span class="line"># print(&quot;面积:%.2f 周长:%.2f&quot;%(area, len))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">b = long(123)</span><br><span class="line">print(type(b))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>参考文档：<br><a href="https://github.com/EtcFly/Python-100-Days/blob/master/Day01-15/02.%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0.md">1、语言元素</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
